name: Snowflake
description:
SNOWFLAKE - follow your feet...

...as not all who wander are lost!

Indulge in the magic of 
'priglavke' artefacts, featuring expressive 
tradition in one corner and contemporary 
zeitgeist in the other. 
With a lot of space in between...

'Priglavke' are handmade, traditionally knitted wool socks 
originating from the Balkans. 

For more infos visit my website+blog.

name: Picture Sets
description:
These are limited edition prints from my 'Wander at Large' - travel series.   

Images are 20x20cm (7,87x7,87inch), 
quality-printed on professional heavyweight matte paper 
and ready for framing.
 
1 set = 4 prints
You can choose to either... 
...obtain one of the two main series sets
...or mix your own set of 4 prints by stating the print numbers

from left above: PAPER DOLLS -series
1.Maiko, 2.Closets, 3.Spiderman, 4.Spectators

from the middle: 
5. HongkongHorizont
6. GoldenBuddha, UlanBator
7. Rotating Planes

from left below: ROTATING PLANES-series 
8., 9., 10.

Other dimensions and materials (different paper, canvas, framed, etc.) available on request.

For more images and inspirations visit my website+blog.
